Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.83,0:01:21.08,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以最後的一步決定世界的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:25.06,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}唯一的贏家非我莫屬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.06,0:01:27.59,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}已經親眼見證了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.59,0:01:34.68,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰都無從預知的最佳答案
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.68,0:01:39.60,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是在棋盤上操縱一切的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:42.22,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}掀起思考的鬥爭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.22,0:01:44.76,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}連錯誤也是偽裝的假象
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.76,0:01:47.26,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}直至將死之前都在精心布局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.26,0:01:49.64,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}這是爭搶王位的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:52.23,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}遵從想法與欲望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:54.74,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一次機會 在劫難逃的壞棋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:57.79,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最後機會 勢必要擊潰勁敵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.79,0:01:59.78,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is too late
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.78,0:02:02.72,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}僅憑那種路數根本就無法追及
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:04.86,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is to say
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.86,0:02:10.26,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}將完全勝利緊握在手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.18,0:02:18.08,OP - CN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所有人都已望塵莫及
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.75,0:00:56.77,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is too late
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.77,0:00:59.78,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}そんな手じゃもう追いつけない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.78,0:01:02.00,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}That is to say
