Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.91,0:01:14.83,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}その有り様 this way
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.83,0:01:21.08,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}最後の一手で決める 世界のanswer
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.08,0:01:25.06,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一人のwinner it's me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.06,0:01:27.59,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}この目は見据えた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.59,0:01:34.68,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰も未だ見通せぬ最適解を
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.68,0:01:39.60,OP - JP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全ては盤上支配するgame
